title: Sefer Bet Yiʹsraʾel / ḥeleḳ 1. heʻarot u-veʾurim ba-Gemara uva-posḳim ha-rishonim ṿe-aḥaronim ʻal ḳinyene ishut ṿe-ʻal harbeh miḳtsoʻot ba-Torah me-iti Yiʹsraʾel Zalman Shelomovits
